    "name": "The Tale of Relm",
    "steam_appid": 3204240,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Tale of Relm is a turn-based fantasy RPG inspired by the golden age of the FF series. Lead a unique cast of heroes through an exciting, story-rich adventure in a hand-crafted world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204240/extras/5e34a10eee7c40d2c141b3e6b8bd5764.poster.avif?t=1765210313\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204240/extras/5e34a10eee7c40d2c141b3e6b8bd5764.webm?t=1765210313\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204240/extras/5e34a10eee7c40d2c141b3e6b8bd5764.mp4?t=1765210313\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Tale of Destiny and Discovery</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the mysterious world of Relm, where ancient magic and shadowy forces collide, two unlikely heroes are bound by fate. Princess Celes, awakening to a powerful legacy, and Edge, a boy who escaped the Crudo program, find their destinies intertwined as they confront the corrupting Black Essence.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204240/extras/2dd794b222ec1959e104bed89e9702b3.poster.avif?t=1765210313\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204240/extras/2dd794b222ec1959e104bed89e9702b3.webm?t=1765210313\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204240/extras/2dd794b222ec1959e104bed89e9702b3.mp4?t=1765210313\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Explore, Discover and Interact</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From quiet villages to forgotten temples, exploration is at the heart of Relm.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Talk to villagers, uncover secrets, solve puzzles inspired by early Zelda games, and piece together the lore of a world on the edge of collapse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shops, NPCs, and hidden clues breathe life into every corner.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204240/extras/801fa428ddefa76055c96cd94885748c.poster.avif?t=1765210313\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204240/extras/801fa428ddefa76055c96cd94885748c.webm?t=1765210313\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204240/extras/801fa428ddefa76055c96cd94885748c.mp4?t=1765210313\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Tactical Encounters</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combat isn’t about grinding - it’s about mastery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enemies are visible on the map, giving you the freedom to engage when you decide. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Break Shield Turn-Based Combat: The battle system is rooted in classic turn-based mechanics, but with a twist; turns aren't set in stone. You’ll need to discover enemy weaknesses, break their shields, and deliver the finishing blow, inspired by the Octopath Traveler system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strategic Boss Battles: Every boss has a perfect strategy waiting to be uncovered, rewarding careful observation and tactical thinking.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204240/extras/03ded6b828e070d17f76241f978b2339.poster.avif?t=1765210313\" width=708 height=398 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204240/extras/03ded6b828e070d17f76241f978b2339.webm?t=1765210313\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204240/extras/03ded6b828e070d17f76241f978b2339.mp4?t=1765210313\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Flexible Character Progression</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level up your heroes your way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A job point system lets you unlock skills in any order, creating countless builds and party combinations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize every hero - from magic-focused mages to battle-hardened warriors - and define your strategy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204240/extras/b7b839638ff85e4fbd87a58f929e43c8.avif?t=1765210313\" width=1209 height=677 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204240/extras/f5111926267b8b0f8e904e1a3f39bb0f.poster.avif?t=1765210313\" width=620 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204240/extras/f5111926267b8b0f8e904e1a3f39bb0f.webm?t=1765210313\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204240/extras/f5111926267b8b0f8e904e1a3f39bb0f.mp4?t=1765210313\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2>",
